# Experiment 4: ML Scoring Evaluation
# All SNDlib instances with benders_standard + 15 ML configurations
# Format: <network_file>;<settings_file>

# Settings configurations:
# 1.  default.toml                       ML Score threshold 0.7,              , 200 stabilization
# 2.  benders_standard.toml              Always solve all subproblems
# 3.  benders_ML-0.7-5C-20S-5R.toml      ML Score threshold 0.7,    5 cuts max,  20 stabilization,         5 root stabilization
# 4.  benders_ML-0.7-10C-20S-5R.toml     ML Score threshold 0.7,   10 cuts max,  20 stabilization,         5 root stabilization
# 5.  benders_ML-0.5-20S.toml            ML Score threshold 0.7,                 20 stabilization          
# 6.  benders_ML-0.5-5C-20S-5R.toml      ML Score threshold 0.5,    5 cuts max,  20 stabilization,         5 root stabilization
# 7.  benders_ML-0.5-10C-20S-5R.toml     ML Score threshold 0.5,   10 cuts max,  20 stabilization,         5 root stabilization
# 8.  benders_ML-0.5-20S.toml            ML Score threshold 0.5,                 20 stabilization
# 9.  benders_ML-5C-20S.toml                                        5 cuts max,  20 stabilization
# 10. benders_ML-10C-20S.toml                                      10 cuts max,  20 stabilization
# 11. benders_ML-P0.3-20S-UR.toml        Prop. of SPs solved 0.3,             ,  20 stabilization, unlimited root stabilization
# 12. benders_ML-P0.5-20S-UR.toml        Prop. of SPs solved 0.5,             ,  20 stabilization, unlimited root stabilization
# 13. benders_ML-P0.7-20S-UR.toml        Prop. of SPs solved 0.7,             ,  20 stabilization, unlimited root stabilization
# 14. benders_ML-P0.3-20S-5R.toml        Prop. of SPs solved 0.3,             ,  20 stabilization,         5 root stabilization
# 15. benders_ML-P0.5-20S-5R.toml        Prop. of SPs solved 0.5,             ,  20 stabilization,         5 root stabilization
# 16. benders_ML-P0.7-20S-5R.toml        Prop. of SPs solved 0.7,             ,  20 stabilization,         5 root stabilization

